{"tid":2200701,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"12青年被扣內地21日  家屬求助港府淪人球「林鄭唔當佢哋係人」","createTime":"2020-09-13T07:27:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-13T08:51:37.000Z","uid":25558,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"d3573b6fcdde2ba795d5702fa2e420eda8427cc5","tid":2200701,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T07:27:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200913/QWLMOWW4ZNBT3ITSH5X5PAQLLQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200913%2FQWLMOWW4ZNBT3ITSH5X5PAQLLQ%2F&d=O8bnHDCsQiwN1SoPxP513VGN3hMT3pF%2B84p80JiLMiI%3D&h=794368da\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200913%2FQWLMOWW4ZNBT3ITSH5X5PAQLLQ%2F&h=2efd0b8c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200913/QWLMOWW4ZNBT3ITSH5X5PAQLLQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n12青年被扣內地21日 <br />\n家屬求助港府淪人球「林鄭唔當佢哋係人」<br />\n<br />\n【徬徨失措】<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：蓬佩奧質疑特首違保護港人承諾<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】12名在反修例運動中被捕的青年上月23日疑偷渡往台灣途中，被廣東海警拘捕，扣留21日仍音訊全無。其中六名被捕人士的家屬昨召開記者會，控訴在尋求多個內地及本港政府部門協助時慘成人球，各部門愛理不理，即使家屬找到律師也不能與當事人會面。家屬批評林鄭月娥政府「當佢哋（被扣押者）唔係人」。協助家屬的民主黨涂謹申指，林鄭有必要保障被扣押港人的合法權益，並促請警方盡快要求內地交還12人給香港。<br />\n<br />\n包括涉違反港版國安法的「香港故事」成員李。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：台記者認助五港人偷渡<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/RUV48g53p7NDNKm0tL9360-fKlI=/3986x2657/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/WTGRIE7TWBAB7MLSYABGMTEZVY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FRUV48g53p7NDNKm0tL9360-fKlI%3D%2F3986x2657%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FWTGRIE7TWBAB7MLSYABGMTEZVY.jpg&h=52d4a4b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■被內地扣留港青的家屬昨召開記者會控訴求助無門，有家屬不禁低頭拭淚，亦有家屬互相緊握雙手以作安慰。許頌明攝<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n內地稱無法核實身份阻見<br />\n<br />\n家屬昨提出四大訴求，包括促請當局讓家屬委託律師與拘留者會面；要求中國當局提供合適藥物給被拘留者；准許被拘留者致電家屬；要求港府確保港人權利獲保障，並立即將12人由內地接回香港。<br />\n<br />\n過去兩周，家屬多次向內地。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n他其後致電香港駐粵經濟貿易辦事處，駐粵辦建議家屬聽從公安要求找律師。已。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n另一被捕者鄧棨然的弟弟透露，哥哥患有哮喘及皮膚病，每日均需要吸入哮喘藥物。他說曾向內地的聯絡人表達哥哥的病情及藥物需要，但對。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n鄧棨然的弟弟批評，林鄭月娥曾自稱港人母親，若為母者發現兒子走失，勢會用盡。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n被捕者李子賢的媽媽指，這是12條人命，特區政府卻不聞不問，她斥林鄭政府不視被扣押的港青是人，「我覺得佢哋（林鄭政府）當佢。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n涂謹申促探訪 駐粵辦迴避<br />\n<br />\n涂謹申指， 2018年四名港人在菲律賓因藏毒罪被判囚終身，林鄭當時多次去信菲律賓政府表達關注，亦有促請中國駐菲律賓大使探望在囚港人表達關心，做法積極，但今次事件做法明顯不同，例如他曾寫信請駐粵辦到鹽田看守所探訪12名港人，可是駐粵辦都在回信時迴避有關問題。<br />\n<br />\n涂謹申又指，林鄭有必要保障被扣。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/6faRN48gB31YM71sfkTLKmbyF1A=/784x1080/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/KARPJ7337ZFRXIA5PZ3ACAULZU.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F6faRN48gB31YM71sfkTLKmbyF1A%3D%2F784x1080%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FKARPJ7337ZFRXIA5PZ3ACAULZU.gif&h=f80836c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/BXieXbQx-iNKPChhbDu0XZA9OBE=/768x1080/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/N3RUUHPGZNGBRNTQUNGKXXL4GA.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FBXieXbQx-iNKPChhbDu0XZA9OBE%3D%2F768x1080%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FN3RUUHPGZNGBRNTQUNGKXXL4GA.gif&h=2ff5e4c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/HZ_iuXQZc2_eJPEKr54ONw4JXD8=/914x2124/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/AKOYU7XL3NDS5H5OQ3UQKNYNFI.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FHZ_iuXQZc2_eJPEKr54ONw4JXD8%3D%2F914x2124%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledail